---
title: Sriracha Teriyaki Double Salmon Bowls with Edamame and Pickled Radishes
description: Get ready to wake up your taste buds with our Sriracha Teriyaki Salmon Bowls. Succulent salmon is smothered in an umami-rich, sweet and spicy sauce and served with black sesame studded rice, sautéed cabbage, edamame and vibrant pickled radishes. Dinner just got interesting.
